						<summary>

						<p>This inscription refers to the construction of <hi rend="italic">maṇḍapa</hi> besides setting up of an image in it. Mentions Sundarachōḻapuram, <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Dēsiyugaṇḍapaṭṭanam, which was a village in Teṉ-kōnāḍu, a sub-division of Olliyūrkūṟṟam.</p>						

